README of the play application
=================================

Pre-requisites: 
	Play framework (activator)
	
Steps and different methodologies to run the project.

	Start the application in dev mode:
		activator run
		
	Start the application without dev mode:
		activator start
	
	Start the application in debug mode:
		activator -jvm-debug 9999 run
		
	Production packaging of the application:
		activator dist
	
	Create the web archive deployment module:
		activator war
	
	Simple execution of the unit tests:
	    activator test
